if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad8ac6d865cbbe43fa77d27569bcf1c3d2c86bfc","tid":2409044,"uid":391702,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T00:03:42.000Z","msg":"識得好多食齋都唔會介意同人share一個pot, 其他人煮肉，自己煮齋咪ok.<br />\n<br />\n當然自己喺屋企煮可以揀擇啲，小心啲。<br />\n<br />\n但同人食嘢都係隨心就可以。食藥嘅膠囊都唔係齋! 有心盡做便ok.<br />\n<br />\n佛祖化緣都唔會因為有肉而浪費食物。<br />\n<br />\n當然，唔係所有人都係因為宗教原因食素，所以都要尊重佢食齋/素嘅原因。<br />\n<br />\n其實，扮肉嘅食物，動機係有啲奇怪，但食落又幾好食。<br />\n<br />\n有時特意一餐唔食肉，俾啲心思去睇個menu, 您會發現原來唔係淨係有羅漢齋一味，可能會發現新天地。"},{"pid":"53b0366747eff0534aa0f9b1efb00bd062aa05bb","tid":2409044,"uid":126325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T13:53:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e446a03369d2ffc8a3fb7be06ef694e82a5318","tid":2409044,"uid":251736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3f0b7283598f6707041a1c7a963e78530984615c","tid":2409044,"uid":21757,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T14:02:28.000Z","msg":"未算<br />\n連動物衍生出來都唔食嗰啲先煩<br />\n會問到一淸二楚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T13:57:07.000Z","msg":"番茄有蠍子同三文魚基因<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6fdd4382bcf54a0f08a49e15d3835065b1876cd","tid":2409044,"uid":99700,"like":6,"dislike":7,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T13:59:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aeMsnV7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaeMsnV7.jpg&h=dfd2677d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"101091dd43ac001593f410a68cb8757287323f50","tid":2409044,"uid":108022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T14:08:05.000Z","msg":"環豚，極端食齋友，婦聯，芝麻仁<br />\n世界4大奇珍異獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8fc3b4c7e237f93f85db88b616a953bfd964c9e","tid":2409044,"uid":21757,"like":2,"dislik